0.1.name: wordpress/wordpress-football-leagues
0.1.description: Wordpress Football Leagues allows you to select a football league to show on you site as a widget. You can select the number of teams to show, thus allowing the widget to be placed is small footers. The widget is currently limited to the English professional leagues. New leagues will be added in future releases.
